<item>
            <title>[LU-1899] Test failure on test suite sanity, subtest test_17m</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1899</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Minh Diep &amp;lt;mdiep@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7ec0dbc2-ff7b-11e1-87b9-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7ec0dbc2-ff7b-11e1-87b9-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_17m failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;e2fsck should not report error upon  short/long symlink MDT: rc=4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 17m&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="15889">LU-1899</key>
            <summary>Test failure on test suite sanity, subtest test_17m</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
